A-nold is back and this time he's a dorf who isn't going to screw up his mission for the 4th time. John Connor is going to receive a beatdown, finally.<br />
<br />
<A HREF=" http://fohguild.org/news/GoblinShredder.jpg"><img src= http://fohguild.org/news/GoblinShredder.jpg border=0 width=320 height=240></A><br />
What a Colonoscopy would feel like in World of Warcraft. Eat your Wheaties kids, you don't want this up your ass.</font>
			
